      <title>乌克兰击落俄罗斯对基辅的所有导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eight-injured-in-new-russian-missile-attack-on-kyiv-mayor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰空军击落了俄罗斯自2月份以来对基辅的首次大规模袭击中发射的全部31枚导弹，这表明尽管延迟接受军事援助，首都的防空能力仍然强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/eight-injured-in-new-russian-missile-attack-on-kyiv-mayor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:01:57 GMT</pubDate>
